entries.journal_entry_completion_summary: You silenced a desert swooper leader and his gang of elite desert swoopers.
entries.journal_entry_description: There is a camp of desert swoopers just outside of Mos Eisley. Teach them to have more respect.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Defeat some desert swoopers and teach them to leave the citizens of Mos Eisley alone.
entries.task01_comm_message_text: Well, it looks like you can handle yourself quite well in combat. Good, because next you're going up against a desert swooper leader and his elite swoopers.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Desert swoopers roam around freely being a nuisance and harassing the people of Mos Eisley. Defeat a camp of desert swoopers.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: Return to Peawp R'dawc and let her know that you've defeated the desert swooper leader.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Taking down the leadership of the desert swoopers always sends them into a tail spin. Eliminate one of the desert swooper leaders.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Fight some elite desert swoopers and teach them to leave the citizens of Mos Eisley alone.
